{"tid":2514921,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"星患者來自港 氣泡現暗湧  首兩周機位爆滿 旅團料暑假成行","createTime":"2021-05-03T14:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T14:29:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ca32b9cc4df1252565cf73189d2ee02c9b25942d","tid":2514921,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:28:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/OGC6PWZXLBGRRCI2FMS4ONYVDQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FOGC6PWZXLBGRRCI2FMS4ONYVDQ%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOFpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=f91a03cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FOGC6PWZXLBGRRCI2FMS4ONYVDQ%2F&h=9fe5a1bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/OGC6PWZXLBGRRCI2FMS4ONYVDQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n星患者來自港 氣泡現暗湧 <br />\n首兩周機位爆滿 旅團料暑假成行<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MOMABK7wHynlupZlXVky0IfCFhI=/510x340/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CV2XYKRTUFEVJJGDWJBHWSW4JY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMOMABK7wHynlupZlXVky0IfCFhI%3D%2F510x340%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCV2XYKRTUFEVJJGDWJBHWSW4JY.jpg&h=11177e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■本港與新加坡將啟動旅遊氣泡，惟兩地疫情反覆，或令計劃添變數。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】疫潮曠日持久，港人坐困疫城，香港與新加坡旅遊氣泡最快本月26日啟動，惟兩地疫情反覆，新加坡前日錄得一宗來自香港的確診個案，料為本港的「輸出個案」，令氣泡啟動再添變數。新加坡交通部稱，已預期疫情有高低，會密切留意兩地疫情發展對旅遊氣泡的影響。商經局亦稱會與新加坡政府保持溝通。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：15萬外勞確診 新加坡無逼接種<br />\n<br />\n新加坡前日新增25宗輸入個案，包括一名44歲由香港回國的新加坡居民，該名男患者無病徵，前日確診。新加坡交通部回覆本報查詢時表示，正密切留意兩地疫情，已預期疫情會有起伏，因此將啟動旅遊氣泡時間定於公佈計劃的一個月後。<br />\n<br />\n商經局亦回覆，一直與新加。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：否認員工為錢打針 譽宴：唔係咁低能<br />\n<br />\n民主黨醫療政策副發言人袁海文表示，若只涉一宗個案且可追蹤到，則仍。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n專家：本地傳播鏈未斷<br />\n<br />\n呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超認為，香港輸出一宗個案即代表本地傳播鏈未斷，一旦短期內再有個案輸出，即反映香港疫情嚴重。「我哋輸出個案其實等如本地源頭不明個案，短時間內如果有兩班機乘客都確診，已經係高危」。本港與新加坡去年底曾訂立旅遊氣泡，惟因疫情爆發而中止。<br />\n<br />\n旅遊業議會主席黃進達在商台節目表示，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n黃又表示，建立旅遊氣泡是大趨勢，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n本地遊方面，港府早前宣佈在疫苗氣泡下可恢復舉辦上限30人的旅行團，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/whH13Birn2LtU61sybc-XF0aQTs=/510x342/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/36OOWW6CZJBIZHSWEG66263ZJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwhH13Birn2LtU61sybc-XF0aQTs%3D%2F510x342%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F36OOWW6CZJBIZHSWEG66263ZJM.jpg&h=21c87875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃進達"},{"pid":"d167dda9ab1b800ce2eabbdfe9b37ef97b5834d5","tid":2514921,"uid":224533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWjiJLQD77HA7MDW7cnn5tb2o9ZFAmjpeQzgZUuBzGeyw?filename=7RaS4q7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7RaS4q7.png&h=d48de47a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}